Portions of the following files are derived from or modeled after ManagedShell
(C# / .NET), and have been reimplemented in Python. These files have been
modified from the original ManagedShell sources:

  - remoteappdock/win32/structs.py
      NOTIFYICONDATA / SHELLTRAYDATA / TRAYITEM structure layouts, modeled after
      ManagedShell Interop.NativeMethods.Shell32 and WindowsTray.ExplorerTrayService.

  - remoteappdock/services/tray_service.py
      Shell_TrayWnd tray host, WM_COPYDATA notification-icon protocol handling,
      and field-merge logic, modeled after ManagedShell WindowsTray.NotificationArea
      and TrayService.

  - remoteappdock/services/explorer_helper.py
      Explorer taskbar hide/restore logic, modeled after ManagedShell
      Common.Helpers.ExplorerHelper.

  - remoteappdock/services/explorer_tray_service.py
      Cross-process enumeration of the existing Explorer tray toolbar, modeled
      after ManagedShell WindowsTray.ExplorerTrayService.

